Instructions for running the project
1. Navigate to the project directory after cloning from Github in a terminal(commands will be used in a GitBash terminal): 
Command for cloning the git repo: git clone https://github.com/ITSC4155Group13/ITSC4155_MDSp24_Group13.git
2. Activate venv with the command: . venv/Scripts/activate (space is important)
3. Install project dependencies with the command: pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run the project with the command: flask run OR python -m flask run
5. Ctrl click the address to follow the link into a web browser
